---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'Introducing Claude Design by Anthropic Labs';
const description = 'Claude Design 让设计师能够广泛探索创意方向，也让非设计背景的创始人、产品经理和营销人员能够轻松制作视觉作品。';
---

<Layout 
  title={title}
  description={description}
  type="article"
  publishedTime="2026-04-20"
  tags={["AI-Design", "Claude", "Product-Launch"]}
>
  <article class="article-content">
    <h1 class="lang-content lang-zh active">Anthropic 发布 Claude Design：AI 时代的视觉设计工具</h1>
    <h1 class="lang-content lang-en">Introducing Claude Design by Anthropic Labs</h1>
    
    <time datetime="2026-04-20">2026-04-20</time>
    
    <div class="lang-content lang-zh active">
      <p>今天，Anthropic Labs 正式推出 Claude Design，这是一款基于 Claude Opus 4.7 视觉模型的协作式设计工具。用户可以通过自然语言描述需求，Claude 会立即生成第一版设计，然后通过对话、评论、直接编辑或自定义滑块进行迭代优化。</p>
      <p>Claude Design 支持多种场景：</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>真实原型</strong>：设计师可将静态 mockup 转为可交互原型，无需代码审查</li>
        <li><strong>产品线框图</strong>：产品经理快速绘制功能流程，直接交给 Claude Code 实现</li>
        <li><strong>设计探索</strong>：快速生成多个设计方向进行对比</li>
        <li><strong>演示文稿</strong>：几分钟内从大纲生成完整 PPTX 或 Canva 文件</li>
        <li><strong>营销物料</strong>：创建落地页、社交媒体素材和 campaign 视觉</li>
      </ul>
      <p>当接入设计系统后，Claude 能自动应用品牌规范，确保输出与公司其他设计保持一致。目前已在 Claude Pro、Max、Team 和 Enterprise 计划中逐步开放。</p>
      <p><a href="https://www.anthropic.com/news/claude-design-anthropic-labs" target="_blank">阅读原文</a></p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="lang-content lang-en">
      <p>Today, Anthropic Labs launched Claude Design, a visual design tool powered by Claude Opus 4.7. Users describe what they need in natural language, and Claude builds the first version instantly. Then refine through conversation, comments, direct edits, or custom sliders.</p>
      <p>Claude Design supports multiple use cases:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Realistic prototypes</strong>: Turn static mockups into interactive prototypes without code review</li>
        <li><strong>Product wireframes</strong>: PMs sketch feature flows and hand off to Claude Code</li>
        <li><strong>Design explorations</strong>: Quickly generate multiple directions to compare</li>
        <li><strong>Pitch decks</strong>: Go from outline to complete PPTX or Canva in minutes</li>
        <li><strong>Marketing collateral</strong>: Create landing pages, social assets, and campaign visuals</li>
      </ul>
      <p>When connected to your design system, Claude automatically applies brand guidelines for consistency. Rolling out gradually to Claude Pro, Max, Team, and Enterprise subscribers.</p>
      <p><a href="https://www.anthropic.com/news/claude-design-anthropic-labs" target="_blank">Read the full article</a></p>
    </div>
    
    <a href="/" class="back-link">← Back to articles</a>
  </article>
</Layout>
